text: Victor Crouin (born 16 June 1999 in Marseille) is a French professional squash player. As of November 2019, he was ranked number 55 in the world. Crouin is enrolled in the Harvard University class of 2022 and plays for Harvard's varsity squash team. ==References== == External links == * * Category:1999 births Category:Living people Category:French male squash players Category:Harvard Crimson men's squash players
